## Operation Reference

Use these operations for all backlog interactions. The operation names are abstract — the actual tool names and parameters are mapped through the backlog registry.

### Core Operations (All Tools)

| Operation | MCP Tool | CLI Command | Purpose |
|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| Create task | `{{OP_CREATE_MCP}}` | `{{OP_CREATE_CLI}}` | Create a new task/artifact |
| List tasks | `{{OP_LIST_MCP}}` | `{{OP_LIST_CLI}}` | List tasks with filters |
| Get task | `{{OP_GET_MCP}}` | `{{OP_GET_CLI}}` | Retrieve task details |
| Update task | `{{OP_UPDATE_MCP}}` | `{{OP_UPDATE_CLI}}` | Modify task fields |
| Move task | `{{OP_MOVE_MCP}}` | `{{OP_MOVE_CLI}}` | Change task status |
| Search | `{{OP_SEARCH_MCP}}` | `{{OP_SEARCH_CLI}}` | Full-text search |
| Complete | `{{OP_COMPLETE_MCP}}` | `{{OP_COMPLETE_CLI}}` | Mark task complete |

